        (hurd_slab_free): New function.
	(struct hurd_slab_space): Move from here ...
        * slab.h (struct hurd_slab_space): ... to here.
	(HURD_SLAB_SPACE_INITIALIZER): Defined.
        (hurd_slab_reap): Remove prototype.
	(hurd_slab_free): New prototype.

